question: Which stadium crosses paths with Tampines?
query:
PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q5110386" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:leisure "stadium" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geo:sfIntersects(?rwkt1, ?cwkt1))
}

PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q12684211" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:amenity "hospital" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    BIND(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) AS ?distance)
}
ORDER BY DESC(?distance)
LIMIT 1

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q25247920" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:amenity "theatre" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    BIND(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) AS ?distance)
}
ORDER BY ASC(?distance)
LIMIT 1

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q24932723" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:amenity "prison" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) < 50000)
}

question: Tell me the castle that is closest to Potong Pasir.

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q7235101" .

PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q7876505" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:building "university" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    BIND(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) AS ?distance)
}
ORDER BY ASC(?distance)
LIMIT 1

PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class1 ?class2 WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q4879339" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class1 osmkey:route "road" .
    ?class1 geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    ?class2 osmkey:natural "beach" .
    ?class2 geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt2 .
    FILTER(geo:sfIntersects(?rwkt1, ?cwkt1) && geo:sfIntersects(?rwkt1, ?cwkt2) )
}

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q14489267" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:historic "building" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    BIND(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) AS ?distance)
}
ORDER BY ASC(?distance)
LIMIT 1

PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q16887503" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:waterway "river" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) <= 5000)
}

PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q104535027" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:building "school" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) > 5000)
}

PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q3299213" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:amenity "college" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    BIND(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) AS ?distance)
}
ORDER BY DESC(?distance)
LIMIT 1

PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q7680664" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:man_made "tower" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    BIND(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) AS ?distance)
}
ORDER BY ASC(?distance)
LIMIT 1

PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q3249777" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:building "university" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) <= 5000)
}

PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q1106591" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:historic "fort" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) < 50000)
}

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q7680667" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:water "river" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    BIND(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) AS ?distance)
}
ORDER BY DESC(?distance)
LIMIT 1

PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q5254438" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:building "stadium" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) < 5000)
}

PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q12701480" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:place "island" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    BIND(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) AS ?distance)
}
ORDER BY DESC(?distance)
LIMIT 1

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q6275961" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:amenity "college" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) <= 20000)
}

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q7570048" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:amenity "university" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    BIND(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) AS ?distance)
}
ORDER BY ASC(?distance)
LIMIT 1

}

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

ASK WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q4986902" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:historic "castle" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geo:sfIntersects(?cwkt1,?rwkt1))
}

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q2224065" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:place "city" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geo:sfTouches(?rwkt1, ?cwkt1))
}

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q1714023" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:building "school" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) <= 20000)
}

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q6315392" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:leisure "park" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) < 50000)
}

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class1 ?class2 WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q1106591" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class1 osmkey:amenity "prison" .
    ?class1 geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    ?class2 osmkey:historic "monument" .
    ?class2 geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt2 .
    FILTER(geo:sfIntersects(?rwkt1, ?cwkt1) && geo:sfIntersects(?rwkt1, ?cwkt2) )
}

question: Which university is the farthest from Jurong Island?

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q985660" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:water "canal" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) <= 20000)
}

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q7876505" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:landuse "forest" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    BIND(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) AS ?distance)
}
ORDER BY DESC(?distance)
LIMIT 1

question: Which college is the closest one to Newton?
query:
PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q6453025" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:amenity "college" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    BIND(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) AS ?distance)
}
ORDER BY ASC(?distance)
LIMIT 1

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q9079137" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:leisure "park" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) < 50000)
}

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q985660" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:place "village" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    BIND(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) AS ?distance)
}
ORDER BY DESC(?distance)
LIMIT 1

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q6015657" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:amenity "bank" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) <= 20000)
}

PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class1 ?class2 WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q6387036" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class1 osmkey:amenity "bank" .
    ?class1 geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    ?class2 osmkey:route "road" .
    ?class2 geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt2 .
    FILTER(geo:sfWithin(?rwkt1, ?cwkt1) && geo:sfWithin(?rwkt1, ?cwkt2) )
}

question: Which city is the furthest from Taman Desa Cemerlang?
